				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1-Ch%C3%BA/B%E1%BB%93-t%C3%A1t-man-Th%C3%A0nh-l%C3%BD-chung/poem-EE2rGBvwXfyuGXZ-9hBiDQ">Bồ tát man - Thành lý chung - 菩薩蠻 - 城裏鐘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1-Ch%C3%BA/author-kEtJEG_ZpvOqTp5qubCKUQ">Hạ Chú</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/%C4%90i%E1%BB%87u-vong/poem-Thq28pggumffsPn3EKlhcg">Điệu vong - 悼亡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/author-og0yg1YWgltsRxS7PoXrcQ">Lâm Hồng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-H%E1%BB%AD/Giang-h%C3%A0nh-v%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-k%E1%BB%B3-039-Y%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BB%AD-ph%E1%BB%A5c-y%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BB%AD/poem-dFkjMBKarneeo43JhRxdoA">Giang hành vô đề kỳ 039 - Yên chử phục yên chử - 江行無題其三十九－煙渚復煙渚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-H%E1%BB%AD/author-mM0fyLflpM7toG9qPE5Qow">Tiền Hử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Giang-th%C3%B4n/poem-juaXNfVOutXCkAADEWiGbw">Giang thôn - 江村</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%C3%AD-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%E1%BB%83-ho%E1%BA%A1-s%C6%A1n-thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-ca/poem-MKjkIOLRJEP7pFkWXlBQtQ">Hí đề Vương Tể hoạ sơn thuỷ đồ ca - 戲題王宰畫山水圖歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/Kinh-Nam-t%C3%ACnh-v%E1%BB%8Dng/poem-9GvtBJjoC9WBB5M_nZRqAQ">Kinh Nam tình vọng - 荊南晴望</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-n8TXz8ZnEQ2g7U6IvK74Vw">Nguyễn Trung Ngạn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-V%C4%83n-Th%E1%BB%8Bnh/K%C3%BD-H%C3%B9ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-th%C6%B0/poem-veP4pOvFWu1QjCr7xukafw">Ký Hùng Bản thư - 寄熊本書</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-V%C4%83n-Th%E1%BB%8Bnh/author-VqxoXqe8mNUs3AHM30fObg">Lê Văn Thịnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/Qu%C3%A1-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90o%C3%A0n/poem-rrqjXrYcit2vGtHGeV_71A">Quá Thành Đoàn - 過城團</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/author-pEICBCCrXfpItm0RL1cOfw">Đinh Nho Hoàn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Ph%C3%A0n-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-tam-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-ph%C3%B3-H%C3%A1n-Trung-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-gV8W2jkzRYVUPWD3eyzNhQ">Tống Phàn nhị thập tam thị ngự phó Hán Trung phán quan - 送樊二十三侍御赴漢中判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-T%C3%B4ng/%E1%BB%A8c-Ti%E1%BB%81n-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-OD314Ox2hEdosNzKXIPsyg">Ức Tiền Đường - 憶錢塘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-T%C3%B4ng/author-0uH2h2ej8qWBk-nTu3RX2Q">Viên Tông</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
